name: Lancer Artoria (Fate/Grand Order) LoRA
description:
LoRA for Artoria Pendragon (Lancer) from Fate Series. Saw there was already another one out there, but figured I'd give it a shot as well. Trained on YesMix with both sfw and nsfw images. Overdetailed her physical appearance so MAY need to use the keywords, will try releasing an updated version without being that specific.

Recommended weight between 0.6-0.8; can go higher or lower depending on additional LoRAs, etc.

Keywords: blonde hair, emerald eyes, braided hair bun, wispy bangs

Without Armor: blue and gold outfit, gold crown

With Armor: blue and gold and silver armor, red cape with white fur, gold crown

Used Hi-Res Fix (Latent) 2x from 512x512 —> Extras (4x-UltraSharp) for final 2048x2048 resolution.
